{"tid":1392262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實好肯定fb係有過濾d“敏感”片同內容","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:43:58.000Z","uid":211933,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f1744c10c8769c39fb80391eb70eb8e5c353303c","tid":1392262,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"沙田714困獸鬥果日我有做過前線拍攝工作（非記者）<br />\n特登開左個fb acc<br />\n記錄低果日警方出爾反爾話唔推進<br />\n結果殺到上沙田市中心既事<br />\nPs:可以起我底做證<br />\n<br />\n內容全部用中性描述去做<br />\n頭一日整好放左link擺連登<br />\n第二日就比fb block左個acc<br />\n第三日我用太空卡認證開返之後，同日下奏再被審查<br />\n直到完全封鎖<br />\n<br />\n唔單止咁，開acc既名<br />\n唔可以出現shatin,沙田，714，遊行，march等字眼<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有留意，好多fb朋友曾經share過既page<br />\n隔一兩日之後就會出現呢句而封左睇唔到：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;會發生此情況 ，通常是因為擁有者僅與一小群用戶分享內容etc&hellip;&hellip;&quot;<br />\n<br />\n尤其是要用電話號碼認證重開acc呢下好撚鬼，一個唔小心或者懶，無買太空卡就好易賴野<br />\n如果fb淪為政治爪牙收集到呢d電話，呢場仗輸左之後<br />\n好有機會成為秋後算帳既工具<br />\n<br />\n呢件事唔可以輕易鬆懈睇少<br />\n如果覺得有用希望大家可以幫推！"},{"pid":"7506c3c7c481ae1c74ad94f2508bd4ab9c97b619","tid":1392262,"uid":31166,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"Facebook奶共"},{"pid":"e174e72493e5668ecd80dd7ea331d7f638331465","tid":1392262,"uid":275317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"唔係有人信fb d澄清？"},{"pid":"64fbc9a5d3865e1372208ff585a2f5ed009f0d12","tid":1392262,"uid":211933,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e174e72493e5668ecd80dd7ea331d7f638331465","tid":1392262,"uid":275317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"唔係有人信fb d澄清？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"一定唔會信既&hellip;不過要提返個現象出尼<br />\n尤其係由69，612開始<br />\n出現&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前無法提供此內容</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n既例子愈尼愈多<br />\n<br />\n我地有時如果碌fb見到d較為少人睇過既證據或者片段<br />\n都要隨時有個準備去back up!<br />\n因為隨時都會被審查block左<br />\n好多人都會睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋無落過電話認證既人，千萬唔好入電話<br />\n大數據時代，入左就係入左<br />\n除非你改電話，否則就算你del acc都無用<br />\nFb一定有底"},{"pid":"17b6fea6aa755f73437efafb54778989b55e070c","tid":1392262,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=7ac496ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"028e790d1e3081e1a141b1596470c5226a907071","tid":1392262,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"自推一次"},{"pid":"9681085dd5448c08246d8abbeacb3059207488ea","tid":1392262,"uid":8880,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"要發起轉用twitter運動<br />\nfacebook實在太撚仆街"},{"pid":"29bb2c30130dd0121102f0233af32f10309dac0d","tid":1392262,"uid":285118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf232175ac3c8bd5daffb7a77e7cd45f2f36597","tid":1392262,"uid":211933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9681085dd5448c08246d8abbeacb3059207488ea","tid":1392262,"uid":8880,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"要發起轉用twitter運動<br />\nfacebook實在太撚仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:32:14.000Z","msg":"其實fb 7分鐘呢單野揚左之後都有諗過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n不過實際真係好難動員得到<br />\nFb用左咁多年好難叫人轉&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n目前能夠做既我覺得只有相關專業人士告fb先可以壓止到個政治審查"},{"pid":"0bf50955fe6bb03dd1645fcaad57bcf48f7678eb","tid":1392262,"uid":158404,"like":3,"d