feafccb443a0b1ac2780607","tid":1392262,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"假acc係好易俾人block<br />\n同埋612之後好多辱警既post都出唔到/俾人del<br />\n大group尤甚，所以佢地努力左del post果d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:00:18.000Z","msg":"就咁睇，香港fb應該多左唔少人手操作去過濾呢方面既野&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n加埋豬西伯格以往歷史<br />\n而宜加既fb又係紅底<br />\n最主要都係想大家小心提防<br />\n<br />\n如果平日拍到一d重要證據同片段<br />\n除左fb之外，應該要用下第二d途徑去傳播或者留底<br />\n<br />\n而經過呢次幾乎同記者一樣既紀事之後<br />\n覺得如果有相關有用資料<br />\n應該要直接搵有權威既機構去幫你傳播<br />\n<br />\n效果一定會更加好，尤其今時今日已經有咁多義士被捉&hellip;"},{"pid":"4f7d0219af5c429c7c82a5d181804119765f4c3a","tid":1392262,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:10:01.000Z","msg":"臨訓前一推，謝謝大家"},{"pid":"ecb2d3ddee9451a3fe783ae9cb7f060324832a7a","tid":1392262,"uid":122988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"之前 Frances hui 條片都係咁"},{"pid":"3579f4fcc74cce4f02f2a225a6148e753aec0a04","tid":1392262,"uid":268978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"仆街FB, 點都要防同做好back up"},{"pid":"f1bab9ccd7186b26808fab3901c57252eb20c806","tid":1392262,"uid":116625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n豬西伯格"},{"pid":"a8ecdfba8c72702508b8231e5587d8b74ac6a914","tid":1392262,"uid":158587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"轉場啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c265154c63288f10857ac3749d7554cb895d1f0","tid":1392262,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf5a93260a7c460450b625b592061b74e87c1bb2","tid":1392262,"uid":52962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":